original_title: Typeoclavecin Film - Variations on the Blues for JoJo #10
overview: Poem by Wanda Phipps (as read by her) and accompanied by the typeoclavecin, a typewriter as a musical instrument, built by the filmmaker for the accompaniment of poets through the technique of dictation.
title: Typeoclavecin Film - Variations on the Blues for JoJo #10
